--- obtain source code ---

download this source code from https://github.com/bgamari/thermostat
e.g. 
git clone git://github.com/bgamari/thermostat.git



--- Install Arduino Libraries ---

Determine the location of your sketchbook by selecting "preferences" on the Arduino menu. 
Create a "libraries" folder in your sketchbook
Download from http://code.google.com/p/xbee-arduino/downloads/list (version 0.4 recommended)
unpack zip and copy XBee folder in the libraries folder


--- Install on Arduino ----
Open thermostat.ino in Arduino IDE
Connect your arduino and click upload
